    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order of monocotyledonous flowering plants, containing 16-24 families, 1,122 genera, and more than 26,000 species. The order has only recently been recognized in classification systems.</Note_Text>
